a kind child.

574
00:55:19,289 --> 00:55:20,754
He's still very kind.

575
00:55:20,856 --> 00:55:25,255
Look what he gave me
and even more.

576
00:55:31,355 --> 00:55:34,117
Come, help me sort
the grain.

577
00:55:40,123 --> 00:55:43,714
with their needs now being
met, Ruth began to feel

578
