Pay him no mind.

624
00:58:03,620 --> 00:58:05,711
He knows nothing about
anything.

625
00:58:05,820 --> 00:58:07,809
He's a fool.

626
00:58:07,920 --> 00:58:12,545
Don't ever allow yourself
to be called a fool.

627
